diff --git a/.thunderdome-output.txt b/.thunderdome-output.txt
new file mode 100644
index 0000000..b35cafc
--- /dev/null
+++ b/.thunderdome-output.txt
@@ -0,0 +1,15 @@
+Fixed 6 bugs:
+
+1. **`src/billing/calculator.ts:20-23`** - Rounding intermediate values caused total drift. Now only rounds final outputs.
+
+2. **`src/billing/service.ts:25`** - `handleRefund` wasn't bound to `this`, causing `this.payments` to be undefined.
+
+3. **`src/inventory/service.ts:50`** - Removed erroneous `status !== 'cancelled'` check that prevented stock release on cancel.
+
+4. **`src/orders/repository.ts:38`** - `update()` replaced entire order instead of merging. Now spreads `existing` first.
+
+5. **`src/orders/service.ts:99`** - Refund window used `>=` instead of `>`, rejecting day-30 refunds.
+
+6. **`src/events/bus.ts:4`** - Global handler map caused cross-test contamination. Changed to instance-level handlers.
+
+All 34 tests pass. Build and lint succeed.
